r.s: PHP extension for interfacing with Redis
r.d: This extension provides an API for communicating with Redis servers.
r.n:
phpredis 5.3.3
This release mostly includes just small PHP 8 Windows compatibility fixes such that pecl.php.net can automatically build Windows DLLs.
You can find a detailed list of changes in Changelog.md and package.xml
* Fix PHP8 Windows includes [270b4db8] (Jan-E) * Fix hash ops for php 8.0.1 [87297cbb] (defender-11) * Disable cloning Redis and RedisCluster objects [cd05a344] (Michael Grunder)
